  "detailed_description": "PixCursor is a pixel art tool that lets you draw pictures by keyboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Edit pictures as same as edit texts.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple, accurate and quick.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Good support for area operation: scale, flip, draw circle/rect/line/curve, etc.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Good support for mutiple frames/layers.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Automatically picks up the color palette.</li></ul>",
